I can step out of this house and get away from the pressures

1765
01:18:46,450 --> 01:18:48,080
和問題, 變成一個完全不同的人
and the problems, be a different man.

1766
01:18:48,080 --> 01:18:50,020
我不用擔心如何修好屋頂
I ain't got to worry about how I'll get the roof fixed,

1767
01:18:50,020 --> 01:18:51,490
或者付錢, 或者...
or pay the bills, or...

1768
01:18:51,490 --> 01:18:53,120
我可以
I can just

1769
01:18:55,020 --> 01:18:57,460
成為一個我前所未有過的自己
be a part of myself I ain't never been before.

1770
01:18:58,530 --> 01:19:01,060
我想知道的是...
What I want to know is...

1771
01:19:03,330 --> 01:19:06,070
我想知道的是
What I want to know

1772
01:19:06,070 --> 01:19:08,540
你是否打算繼續見她?
is do you plan to continue seeing her?

1773
01:19:08,540 --> 01:19:11,170
那就是你可以說的
That's all you can say to me.

1774
01:19:12,270 --> 01:19:14,110
我在她的家裏能放鬆下來
I could sit up in her house and laugh.

1775
01:19:14,110 --> 01:19:16,380
你明白嗎?
You understand what I'm saying?

1776
01:19:16,380 --> 01:19:19,180
我可以放聲笑, 而那感覺真好
I could laugh out loud, and it feels good.

1777
01:19:19,180 --> 01:19:21,380
簡直好到了我心底裏
It reaches all the way down to the bottom of my shoes.

1778
01:19:21,380 --> 01:19:22,580
Rose, 我...
Rose, I...

1779
01:19:25,120 --> 01:19:28,090
我不想放棄那些
I can't give that up.

1780
01:19:33,530 --> 01:19:35,830
那或許你該繼續留在她那裏
Well, maybe you ought to go on and stay down there with her,

1781
01:19:35,830 --> 01:19:37,530
如果她真是比我更好的女人的話
if she's a better woman than me.

1782
01:19:37,530 --> 01:19:39,400
這不是關於誰是更好的女人的問題
It ain't about nobody being a better woman, or nothing.

1783
01:19:39,470 --> 01:19:40,470
Rose, 你盡責了
Rose, you ain't to blame.

1784
01:19:40,500 --> 01:19:43,270
做妻子的話你簡直是不二之選
A man couldn't ask for a better wife than you've been.

1785
01:19:43,270 --> 01:19:44,780
這事我得負起所有責任
I'm responsible for it.

1786
01:19:44,780 --> 01:19:46,810
我每天重複做著同樣的事
I done locked myself into a pattern,

1787
01:19:46,810 --> 01:19:48,480
照顧你們, 都讓我忘了自己了
trying to take care of you all, that I forgot about myself.

1788
01:19:48,480 --> 01:19:50,280
我不是一直在你背後嗎?
Well, what the hell was I there for?

1789
01:19:50,280 --> 01:19:51,850
那是我的工作, 不是他人的
That was my job, not somebody else's.

1790
01:19:51,850 --> 01:19:55,150
Rose, 聽著, 我竭盡所能去過正當的生活
Rose, listen to me. I done tried all my life to live decent.

1791
01:19:55,150 --> 01:19:58,150
一個正當, 努力向上的生活
To live a clean, hard, useful life.

1792
01:19:58,150 --> 01:20:01,320
我盡了力去成為一個好丈夫
I try to be a good husband to you, in every way I know how.

1793
01:20:01,320 --> 01:20:03,490
可能我一開始就錯了吧, 我不知道
Maybe I come into the world backwards, I don't know,

1794
01:20:03,490 --> 01:20:07,130
但你就像上場前已經被二振了一樣
but you're born with two strikes on you before you come to the plate.

1795
01:20:07,200 --> 01:20:08,200
你得把任何事都看管好
You got to guard it closely,

1796
01:20:08,230 --> 01:20:10,870
老是擔心突發事情
always looking for the curveball on the inside corner.

1797
01:20:10,870 --> 01:20:12,530
你不能讓任何事不受你控制
You can't afford a called strike.

1798
01:20:12,540 --> 01:20:14,170
你不能讓任何事漏掉
You can't let nothing get past you.

1799
01:20:14,170 --> 01:20:16,300
要是你倒下了, 你還不死心
If you're going down, you're doing down swinging.

1800
01:20:16,310 --> 01:20:19,210
所有事都像對著你干一樣
Everything lined up against you!

1801
01:20:20,580 --> 01:20:22,310
你還想怎樣?
What you gonna do?

1802
01:20:23,650 --> 01:20:26,350
我贏了他們, Rose, 我短打了 [犧牲]
I fooled them, Rose. I bunted.

1803
01:20:26,580 --> 01:20:30,520
當我有你和Cory和份有點像樣的工作, 我很安全
When I found you and Cory and a halfway decent job, I was safe.

1804
01:20:30,520 --> 01:20:32,850
沒什麼可以拖累我了
Couldn't nothing touch me!

1805
01:20:32,860 --> 01:20:34,420
我不會再被三振出局
I wasn't gonna strike out no more.

1806
01:20:34,420 --> 01:20:35,860
不會再回去坐牢
I wasn't going back to the penitentiary.

1807
01:20:35,860 --> 01:20:38,330
不會再喝醉, 睡在街上
I wasn't gonna lie in the street with a bottle of wine.

1808
01:20:38,330 --> 01:20:42,600
我安全了, 我有個家庭, 有份工作
I was safe. I had me a family, a job.

1809
01:20:43,630 --> 01:20:46,500
我不會被三振的
I wasn't gonna get that last strike.

1810
01:20:48,340 --> 01:20:51,270
我站在一壘
I was standing on first base,

1811
01:20:51,270 --> 01:20:54,310
等著回到本壘
waiting for one of them boys to
knock me in, to bring me home.

1812
01:20:54,310 --> 01:20:55,180
你該留在我們的床上, Troy
You should have stayed in my bed, Troy.

1813
01:20:55,180 --> 01:20:57,210
然後我看到那女子, 她讓我膽大起來
Then I saw the gal, she firmed up my backbone.

1814
01:20:57,210 --> 01:20:59,580
我在想如果我努力點, 或許可以盜壘
I got to thinkin' that if I tried, maybe I could steal second.

1815
01:20:59,580 --> 01:21:01,380
- 你明白嗎?   - 你該抱緊我
- You understand what I'm saying? - You should've held me tight.

1816
01:21:01,380 --> 01:21:03,680
你該捉緊我的手
You should've grabbed me and held on.

1817
01:21:03,690 --> 01:21:04,620
我站在一壘18年了
I stood on first base for 18 years,

1818
01:21:04,620 --> 01:21:07,260
然後我想, 管他的, 豁出去
and I thought, well, god damn it, go on for it!

1819
01:21:07,260 --> 01:21:09,590
我們不是在說棒球啊!
We ain't talking about baseball!

1820
01:21:09,590 --> 01:21:12,190
我們在說你跟別的女人鬼混
We talking about you going off and laying up with another woman,

1821
01:21:12,200 --> 01:21:13,230
然後把這事帶回家跟我說
then bringing it home to me.

1822
01:21:13,230 --> 01:21:14,360
那才是我們要討論的
That's what we're talking about.

1823
01:21:14,360 --> 01:21:17,470
- 我們不是要談棒球!   - Rose, 你沒細心聽
- We're not talkin' about no baseball! - Rose, you're not listening to me.

1824
01:21:17,500 --> 01:21:19,630
我在用我最擅長的東西去表達
I'm trying to explain it to you the best way I know how.

1825
01:21:21,300 --> 01:21:22,800
對我來說很難去接受
It's not easy for me to admit

1826
01:21:22,800 --> 01:21:25,670
我站在原地18年了這事實
that I've been standing in the same place for 18 years!

1827
01:21:25,680 --> 01:21:28,410
我也跟你一起站在原地啊!
Well, I've been standing with you!

1828
01:21:28,410 --> 01:21:32,480
我一直都跟你站在原地, Troy! 我也有我的人生
I've been right here with you, Troy! I got a life, too.

1829
01:21:32,480 --> 01:21:36,680
我為此付出了我的18年啊
I gave 18 years of my life to stand in the same spot as you!

1830
01:21:36,690 --> 01:21:38,720
你沒想過我也想要做其他事?
Don't you think I ever wanted other things?

1831
01:21:38,720 --> 01:21:41,220
沒想過我也有我的夢想和願望?
Don't you think I had dreams and hopes?

1832
01:21:41,220 --> 01:21:43,660
那我的生命呢? 那我呢?
What about my life? What about me?

1833
01:21:43,660 --> 01:21:45,260
你以為我沒有想過
Don't you think it ever crossed my mind

1834
01:21:45,260 --> 01:21:46,430
去認識其他男人?
to want to know other men?

1835
01:21:46,430 --> 01:21:49,200
或者一走了之
That I wanted to lay up somewhere

1836
01:21:49,200 --> 01:21:50,700
忘了我的職責?
and forget about my responsibilities?

1837
01:21:50,700 --> 01:21:52,500
或者我想有過人讓我笑
That I wanted someone to make me laugh,

1838
01:21:52,500 --> 01:21:54,570
讓我快樂?
so I could feel good?

1839
01:21:54,570 --> 01:21:56,670
你不是唯一一個有需求的人
You're not the only one who's got wants and needs.

1840
01:21:56,670 --> 01:21:58,670
但我留下來了, Troy
But I held on to you, Troy.

1841
01:21:58,680 --> 01:22:03,210
我把我的所有情感, 需求和夢想
I took all my feelings, my wants and needs and dreams,

1842
01:22:03,210 --> 01:22:04,950
埋藏在你的心底下
and I buried them inside you.

1843
01:22:04,950 --> 01:22:07,380
我把種子埋藏好, 每天看著它, 祈望它成長
I planted a seed and watched and prayed over it.

1844
01:22:07,380 --> 01:22:10,420
我把自己埋藏在你心內然後等待開花!
I planted myself inside you and waited to bloom!

1845
01:22:10,420 --> 01:22:12,290
但那花了我18年時間
And it didn't take me no 18 years

1846
01:22:12,290 --> 01:22:14,390
才知道那泥土原來如石頭般硬
to realize the soil was hard and rocky,

1847
01:22:14,390 --> 01:22:16,490
還有它根本不會開花!
and it wasn't never gonna bloom!

1848
01:22:16,490 --> 01:22:19,490
但我仍然捉緊你, 我把你捉得更緊
But I held on to you, Troy. I held you tighter.

1849
01:22:19,500 --> 01:22:21,560
你是我的丈夫
You was my husband.

1850
01:22:21,560 --> 01:22:24,370
我該給你我的全部
I owed you everything I had.

1851
01:22:24,370 --> 01:22:27,240
我的每一部分
Every part of me I could find to give you.

1852
01:22:27,240 --> 01:22:30,970
當晚上我在樓上的睡房時
And upstairs in that bedroom, with the darkness falling in on me,

1853
01:22:30,970 --> 01:22:35,310
我用盡力氣消除那個疑慮
I gave everything I had to try and erase the doubt

1854
01:22:35,310 --> 01:22:37,780
那個其實你不是個好男人的疑慮
that you wasn't the finest man in the world.

1855
01:22:37,780 --> 01:22:40,650
無論你打算去哪裏, 我都會跟著你
And wherever you was going, i was gonna be there with you,

1856
01:22:40,650 --> 01:22:43,380
因為你是我的丈夫
because you was my husband.

1857
01:22:44,590 --> 01:22:47,660
因為這樣做我才能繼續做你的妻子
'Cause that's the only way I was gonna survive as your wife.

1858
01:22:48,720 --> 01:22:51,330
你經常說給什麼
You always talking about what you give

1859
01:22:51,330 --> 01:22:52,630
還有你不能給什麼
and what you don't have to give.

1860
01:22:53,330 --> 01:22:55,000
但你也會拿取, Troy
But you take, too, Troy.

1861
01:22:55,000 --> 01:22:57,670
你會拿取而且不在乎是誰付出的
You take and don't even know nobody's giving.

1862
01:22:57,670 --> 01:22:59,730
你說我好逸惡勞
You say I take and don't give.

1863
01:22:59,810 --> 01:23:00,910
- Troy, 你弄痛我了   - 你說我好逸惡勞
- Troy, you're hurting me.   - You say I take and don't give.

1864
01:23:00,940 --> 01:23:02,400
- Troy, 我的手很痛, 放手!   - 我給了我能給的
- Troy, you're hurting my arm, let go!
- I gave you everything I got.

1865
01:23:02,410 --> 01:23:03,470
別說我沒有
Don't you tell that lie on me.

1866
01:23:03,470 --> 01:23:04,770
- 媽媽!   - 別說我沒有
- Mama!   - Don't you tell that lie!

1867
01:23:04,770 --> 01:23:06,540
Troy, 我弄痛我了!
Troy, you're hurting me!

1868
01:23:07,010 --> 01:23:08,510
Troy! Troy!
Troy! Troy!

1869
01:23:08,710 --> 01:23:12,550
好了, 那是二振
All right. That's strike two.

1870
01:23:13,380 --> 01:23:17,590
你別再惹我, 你最好別三振
You stay away from around me, boy. Don't you strike out.

1871
01:23:19,320 --> 01:23:21,390
你滿球數了
You're living with a full count.

1872
01:23:24,660 --> 01:23:26,630
你最好別三振!
Don't you strike out!

1873
01:26:46,930 --> 01:26:48,900
Troy, 我想跟你說點事
Troy, I want to talk to you.

1874
01:26:51,600 --> 01:26:53,770
突然間?
All of a sudden?

1875
01:26:55,670 --> 01:26:58,040
過了這麼久你想跟我說點事?
After all this time, you want to talk to me, huh?

1876
01:26:59,040 --> 01:27:00,740
你數個月來沒跟我說過一句話
You ain't wanted to talk to me in months.

1877
01:27:00,740 --> 01:27:02,010
昨晚也沒有
You ain't wanted to talk to me last night.

1878
01:27:02,010 --> 01:27:03,740
你那時可不想理會我
You didn't want no parts of me then.

1879
01:27:04,250 --> 01:27:06,510
現在你想來說什麼?
What you want to talk to me about now?

1880
01:27:09,850 --> 01:27:11,590
明天是星期五
Tomorrow's Friday.

1881
01:27:11,590 --> 01:27:12,890
我知道
I know what day tomorrow is.

1882
01:27:12,890 --> 01:27:14,920
你以為我不知道嗎?
You think I don't know tomorrow's Friday?

1883
01:27:14,920 --> 01:27:17,590
我的整生, 都在等星期五的來臨
My whole life, I ain't done nothing but look to see Friday coming,

1884
01:27:17,590 --> 01:27:18,260
你還來提醒我
and you got to tell me it's Friday.

1885
01:27:18,260 --> 01:27:19,590
我想知道你會否回家
I want to know if you're coming home.

1886
01:27:19,900 --> 01:27:22,600
我每天都回家, 你知道的
I always come home, Rose. You know that.

1887
01:27:22,600 --> 01:27:23,860
沒有一晚我是沒回來的
Ain't never been a night I ain't come home.

1888
01:27:23,870 --> 01:27:25,800
你明知道那不是我的意思
That ain't what I mean, and you know it.

1889
01:27:25,800 --> 01:27:29,270
我想知道你下班後會否直接回家
I wanna know if you're coming straight home after work.

1890
01:27:29,270 --> 01:27:32,310
我想我會兌換支票, 然後在Taylor的酒吧和他們喝點酒
I figured I'd cash my check,
hang out at Taylors' with the boys.

1891
01:27:32,380 --> 01:27:33,580
或許玩一局[西洋]跳棋
Maybe play a game of checkers.

1892
01:27:33,610 --> 01:27:36,080
Troy, 我不能再繼續這樣, 我接受不了
Troy, I can't live like this. I won't live like this.

1893
01:27:36,080 --> 01:27:37,750
自那之後你就人在心不在
You're living on borrowed time with me.

1894
01:27:37,750 --> 01:27:39,780
六個月以來, 你都沒真正回來
Been going on six months now, you ain't been coming home.

1895
01:27:39,780 --> 01:27:41,880
我每晚都回來, 一年來從沒間斷過
I come home every night. Every night of the year.

1896
01:27:41,880 --> 01:27:44,620
那就整整365天
That's 365 days.

1897
01:27:45,890 --> 01:27:48,690
我想你明天下班後直接回家
I want you to come home tomorrow after work.

1898
01:27:53,630 --> 01:27:57,100
Rose, 你知道我不會亂花錢
Rose, I don't mess up my pay. You know that.

1899
01:27:57,100 --> 01:27:59,070
我收到工資後就全數交給你
I take my pay, i give it to you.

1900
01:27:59,070 --> 01:28:02,740
我只拿著你分配給我的部份
I don't have no money but what you give me back.

1901
01:28:02,740 --> 01:28:05,910
我只想要一點私人時間而已
I just want a little time to myself.

1902
01:28:05,910 --> 01:28:07,070
去享樂一下
A little time to enjoy life.

1903
01:28:07,080 --> 01:28:09,040
那我呢? 何時才輪到我去享樂?
What about me? When's my time to enjoy life?

1904
01:28:09,050 --> 01:28:11,310
我不知道還可以說什麼, 我已經盡力了
I don't know what to tell you, Rose. I'm doing the best I can.

1905
01:28:11,380 --> 01:28:12,680
你下班回家後
You ain't been comin' home from work,

1906
01:28:12,710 --> 01:28:13,880
只換件衣服又出去了
but time enough to change your clothes and run out.

1907
01:28:14,040 --> 01:28:15,950
你叫那盡力嗎?
You wanna call that the best you can do?

1908
01:28:17,590 --> 01:28:20,720
我晚點得去醫院看Alberta
I'm going over to the hospital to see Alberta.

1909
01:28:21,690 --> 01:28:23,360
她今天下午進了醫院
She went into the hospital this afternoon.

1910
01:28:23,360 --> 01:28:26,890
看來是早產
Looks like she might have the baby early.

1911
01:28:27,760 --> 01:28:29,600
我不會去太久
I won't be gone long.

1912
01:28:35,800 --> 01:28:37,710
你該知道他們今天到了Pearl小姐那裏
Well, you ought to know. They went over to Miss Pearl's

1913
01:28:37,780 --> 01:28:38,880
帶走了Gabe
and got Gabe today.

1914
01:28:38,910 --> 01:28:42,810
她說你叫他們鎖起他來
She said you told them to go ahead and lock him up.

1915
01:28:42,810 --> 01:28:46,850
我才沒有說過, 你被她騙了
I ain't said no such thing. Whoever told you that is telling a lie.

1916
01:28:46,850 --> 01:28:48,720
Pearl小姐撒了個很大的謊
Miss Pearl ain't doing nothing but telling a big, fat lie.

1917
01:28:48,720 --> 01:28:50,680
她不用說出口, 我在文件上看到的
She ain't had to tell me. I read it on the papers.

1918
01:28:50,690 --> 01:28:52,820
- 那份文件說了什麼?   - 說你叫他們去帶走他
- What'd it say, huh?   - It said you told them to take him.

1919
01:28:52,820 --> 01:28:54,340
那他們肯定弄錯了
Oh, well, then they screwed that up,

1920
01:28:54,370 --> 01:28:55,860
就像他們弄錯其他事一樣
just like they screw up everything.

1921
01:28:55,890 --> 01:28:56,920
我才不在意他們在文件上說了什麼
I ain't worried about what they got on that paper.

1922
01:28:56,920 --> 01:28:58,390
說政府會把他的部分財產交給醫院作照顧費用
It say the government sends part of the check to the hospital,

1923
01:28:58,460 --> 01:28:59,560
另一部份交給你
the other part to you.

1924
01:28:59,590 --> 01:29:02,130
我跟此事毫無關係
I ain't got nothing to do with that, if that's the way it works.

1925
01:29:02,130 --> 01:29:02,630
我也沒叫他們分給我
I don't make up the rules...

