They got to get all their paperwork straight

2270
01:56:12,590 --> 01:56:13,990
才讓你做任何事
before they let you do anything.

2271
01:56:14,000 --> 01:56:17,430
怎樣都好, 我很高興你趕來了, 他們讓Lyons來
Well, I'm sure glad you made it. They let Lyons come.

2272
01:56:17,500 --> 01:56:18,600
你的叔叔Gabe還在醫院內
Your Uncle Gabe's still in the hospital.

2273
01:56:18,630 --> 01:56:20,700
他們不知道該否讓他出來
They don't know if they're gonna let him out or not.

2274
01:56:20,700 --> 01:56:22,400
我剛跟他們說過話
I talked to them a little while ago.

2275
01:56:22,400 --> 01:56:24,740
美國海軍陸戰隊的下士
A corporal in the United States marines.

2276
01:56:24,740 --> 01:56:27,010
你爸爸早知道你是軍人的材料
Your daddy knew you had it in you.

2277
01:56:27,010 --> 01:56:29,010
他以前總是這樣告訴我
He used to tell me all the time.

2278
01:56:29,010 --> 01:56:31,010
他看上去很不錯吧, Bono先生?
Hey, don't he look good, Mr. Bono?

2279
01:56:31,010 --> 01:56:34,680
對, 他讓我記起我第一次見到的Troy
Yeah, he reminds me of Troy when I first met him.

2280
01:56:35,620 --> 01:56:37,350
我說, Rose
Ah, say, Rose,

2281
01:56:37,350 --> 01:56:39,620
Lucille現在在教堂和唱詩班一起
Lucille's down at the church with the choir.

2282
01:56:39,620 --> 01:56:41,620
我先去跟那些護柩者說一下
I'm gonna go get the pallbearers lined up.

2283
01:56:41,620 --> 01:56:42,820
晚點回來
I'll be back to get you all.

2284
01:56:43,060 --> 01:56:44,490
謝謝, Jim
Thanks, Jim.

2285
01:56:44,490 --> 01:56:45,560
晚點見, Bono先生
See you, Mr. Bono.

2286
01:56:49,530 --> 01:56:52,630
Cory, 看看Raynell
Cory, look at Raynell.

2287
01:56:52,630 --> 01:56:53,730
不是很美嗎?
Ain't she precious?

2288
01:56:53,730 --> 01:56:55,400
她將來定是個大美人
She's gonna break a whole lot of hearts.

2289
01:56:55,540 --> 01:56:57,070
跟你的哥哥打招呼, 這是你的哥哥Cory
Say hello to your brother. This your brother, Cory.

2290
