No, mama, thanks. I don't feel like eating.

2304
01:57:23,760 --> 01:57:24,860
晚點吧
I'll get something later.

2305
01:57:24,870 --> 01:57:28,830
Raynell, get up there and get
that dress on like I told you.

2306
01:57:40,110 --> 01:57:43,450
我早就知道你能成就大事
I always knew you was gonna make something out of yourself.

2307
01:57:44,850 --> 01:57:47,620
你永遠朝著正確的方向走
Your head was always in the right direction.

