So,

2309
01:57:53,390 --> 01:57:54,890
你打算繼續服役嗎?
you gonna stay in?

2310
01:57:54,900 --> 01:57:57,500
讓它成為你的事業? 為軍隊付出20年?
Make it a career? Put in your 20 years?

2311
01:57:57,700 --> 01:58:01,500
我不知道, 已經服役六年了, 我想已經足夠了
I don't know. I got six already. I think that's enough.

2312
01:58:01,500 --> 01:58:05,100
為美國效力然後早早退休
Stick with Uncle Sam and retire early.

2313
01:58:05,110 --> 01:58:06,910
這裏沒有什麼
Ain't nothing out here.

2314
01:58:08,580 --> 01:58:11,510
我想Rose跟你說過我發生什麼事了吧
I guess Rose told you about what happened with me.

2315
01:58:13,780 --> 01:58:16,650
他們現在讓我在囚犯工廠工作
They got me down at the workhouse.

2316
01:58:16,650 --> 01:58:19,520
我自以為偷偷的兌現他人支票很聰明
I thought I was being slick cashing other people's checks.

2317
01:58:20,690 --> 01:58:22,590
被判多少年了?
How much time you doing?

2318
01:58:23,420 --> 01:58:25,790
三年
They give me three years.

2319
01:58:25,790 --> 01:58:28,960
我接受了, 現在只剩九個月
I got that beat now. I ain't got but nine more months.

2320
01:58:34,470 --> 01:58:36,800
那也不是件壞事
It ain't so bad.

2321
01:58:36,800 --> 01:58:39,840
你能學會如何面對它, 像面對其他事一樣
You learn to deal with it like anything else.

2322
