那就是爸爸的座右銘
that's what papa used to say.

2324
01:58:47,550 --> 01:58:51,150
他以前被三振後老是這樣說
He used to say that when he struck out.

2325
01:58:51,150 --> 01:58:53,520
我看見過他被連續三次三振
I seen him strike out three times in a row,

2326
01:58:53,520 --> 01:58:57,720
再上場時, 他把球打到看台上
and the next time up, he hit the ball over the grandstand.

2327
01:58:57,730 --> 01:59:00,760
在霍姆斯特德的棒球場上 [佛羅里達州]
Right out there in Homestead field.

2328
01:59:01,460 --> 01:59:03,430
他打到看台上還不滿意
He wasn't satisfied hitting in the seats.

2329
01:59:03,430 --> 01:59:05,430
他想打出球場外
He wanted to hit it over everything.

2330
01:59:06,670 --> 01:59:08,530
比賽完結後
Then after the game,

2331
01:59:09,840 --> 01:59:14,570
有200位觀眾等著與他握手
he had 200 people standing around, waiting to shake his hand.

2332
01:59:17,780 --> 01:59:20,580
人生不如意事十常八九
You got to take the crookeds with the straights.

2333
01:59:23,950 --> 01:59:25,850
他真與眾不同
Papa was something else.

2334
01:59:26,950 --> 01:59:29,220
你還在玩音樂嗎?
You still playing?

2335
01:59:29,220 --> 01:59:30,920
Cory, 你知道我不會放棄音樂的
Cory, you know I'm gonna do that.

2336
01:59:31,790 --> 01:59:34,190
我跟那裏幾個志同道合的人, 組成了樂隊
We got some fellas down there. We got us a band.

2337
01:59:34,200 --> 01:59:37,230
出獄後我們打算繼續一起表演, 但...
We gonna try to stay together when we get out, but...

2338
01:59:37,230 --> 01:59:38,560
對
Yeah.

2339
01:59:39,800 --> 01:59:41,930
我還在玩音樂
I'm still playing.

2340
01:59:42,600 --> 01:59:44,000
它仍然是我有動力活下去的原因
Still helps me get out of bed in the morning.

2341
01:59:44,070 --> 01:59:45,170
只要它一天是
As long as it do that,

2342
01:59:45,200 --> 01:59:48,870
我就不會放棄它, 更認真對待它
I'm gonna stick with it, try to make some sense out of it.

2343
01:59:48,880 --> 01:59:51,610
Lyons, 我煮了蛋給你
Lyons, I got these eggs in a pan.

2344
01:59:53,710 --> 01:59:55,880
讓我進去吃點什麼, 老兄
Let me get in here and get these eggs, man.

2345
01:59:55,880 --> 01:59:57,950
