Get ready to go bury papa.

2346
02:00:03,890 --> 02:00:05,520
你過得怎樣了?
How you doing?

2347
02:00:06,890 --> 02:00:08,590
你還好嗎?
You doing all right?

2348
02:00:26,250 --> 02:00:28,980
你好
Hi.

2349
02:00:29,920 --> 02:00:31,650
你以前睡在我的房間嗎?
You used to sleep in my room?

2350
02:00:32,790 --> 02:00:34,850
對, 那以前是我的房間
Yeah, that used to be my room.

2351
02:00:35,290 --> 02:00:38,520
那就是爸爸說的, Cory的房間
That's what papa callit. "Cory's room."

2352
02:00:40,660 --> 02:00:42,730
你的美式足球還在櫃裏
Got your football in the closet.

2353
02:00:42,730 --> 02:00:45,830
Raynell, 快換衣服, 也穿上新的鞋子
Raynell. Get up there, get dressed, and put them good shoes on.

2354
02:00:45,830 --> 02:00:48,030
媽媽, 我就不能穿這雙嗎? 那雙新鞋子弄痛我的腳
Mama, can I just wear these? Them others hurt my feet!

2355
02:00:48,040 --> 02:00:50,300
那也只會弄痛一會兒而已
Well, they're just gonna have to hurt your feet for a while.

2356
02:00:50,300 --> 02:00:51,270
你買的時候
You ain't said they hurt your feet

2357
02:00:51,270 --> 02:00:52,740
也沒說它們會弄痛你
when you went down to the store and got 'em.

2358
02:00:52,740 --> 02:00:54,870
那時候不痛, 現在我的雙腳都長大了
They didn't hurt then. My feet done got bigger.

2359
02:00:54,880 --> 02:00:56,680
別給我頂嘴!
Don't give me no back talk!

2360
02:00:56,680 --> 02:00:59,650
快換衣服, 穿上新鞋子
Get up there, get dressed, and put them good shoes on.

2361
02:02:07,010 --> 02:02:09,950
這裏沒什麼大改變
Ain't too much changed.

2362
02:02:09,950 --> 02:02:12,820
那棒球還吊在樹上
He still got that rag tied to the tree.

2363
02:02:15,920 --> 02:02:17,990
他當時在這裏揮棒
He was out here swinging that bat.

2364
02:02:19,660 --> 02:02:22,630
我剛想回去屋子內
I was just getting ready to go back in the house.

2365
02:02:23,700 --> 02:02:26,630
他一揮, 然後整個人就倒下了
He swung that bat and just fell over.

2366
02:02:28,870 --> 02:02:32,840
當他揮棒時, 他看起來好像在笑
Seem like, when he swung it, he stood there with this grin on his face.

2367
02:02:38,710 --> 02:02:40,210
下一秒就倒下了
Then he just fell over.

2368
02:02:43,050 --> 02:02:44,850
他們來把他送到醫院
They carried him down there to the hospital,

2369
02:02:44,850 --> 02:02:46,950
但我知道已經沒有需要了
but I knew there wasn't no need.

2370
02:02:49,420 --> 02:02:50,420
不如跟我進去再說?
Why don't you come on in the house?

2371
02:02:50,420 --> 02:02:53,060
媽媽, 我有點事要告訴你
Mama, I got something to tell you.

2372
02:02:54,390 --> 02:02:57,730
我不知道該怎開口, 但我得告訴你
I don't know how to tell you this, but I got to tell you.

2373
02:02:57,730 --> 02:02:59,800
我不會出席爸爸的葬禮
I'm not going to papa's funeral.

2374
02:03:02,000 --> 02:03:05,900
小子, 閉嘴
Boy, hush your mouth.

2375
02:03:05,910 --> 02:03:08,070
那是你的爸爸!
That's your daddy you talking about!

2376
02:03:08,080 --> 02:03:10,140
我不想在這種時候聽到你說這個
I don't want to hear that kind of talk this morning.

2377
02:03:10,140 --> 02:03:11,780
我這麼辛苦把你養成這樣的嗎?
I done raised you to come to this?

2378
02:03:11,780 --> 02:03:13,510
你健健康康的
You standing there all healthy and grown,

2379
02:03:13,510 --> 02:03:14,980
怎麼說你不出席爸爸的葬禮了?
talking about you ain't going to your daddy's funeral?

2380
02:03:14,980 --> 02:03:17,150
- 媽媽, 聽著   - 我不想聽, Cory!
- Mama, listen... - I don't want to hear it, Cory!

2381
02:03:17,220 --> 02:03:18,420
別再改樣想了
Just get that thought out of your head.

2382
02:03:18,450 --> 02:03:21,220
我得向他說不, 就一次, 我得說不
I've got to say no to him. One time in my life, I got to say no.

2383
02:03:21,220 --> 02:03:22,990
