02:03:32,770 --> 02:03:35,130
不出席你爸爸的葬禮不會讓你成人的
Not going to your daddy's funeral ain't gonna make you a man.

2389
02:03:38,100 --> 02:03:41,110
我以前在這裏的日子
The whole time I was growing up, living in his house,

