It weighed on you, and it sunk into your flesh.

2392
02:03:48,850 --> 02:03:50,880
它會把你緊緊的包著, 不讓你走
It would wrap around you and lay there

2393
02:03:50,880 --> 02:03:53,220
直到你分不清哪個才是真正的自己
until you couldn't tell which one was you anymore.

2394
02:03:53,220 --> 02:03:57,760
那黑影就一點點的侵蝕到你皮下
That shadow just diggin' into your flesh!

2395
02:03:57,760 --> 02:04:00,030
試著佔據你的心, 然後控制你
Trying to crawl in. Trying to live through you.

2396
02:04:00,930 --> 02:04:05,760
哪裏都是Troy Maxson的蹤影
Everywhere I looked, I saw Troy Maxson staring right back at me.

2397
02:04:05,770 --> 02:04:08,930
在你床下, 又或是在衣櫃內
Hiding under the bed, in the closet.

2398
02:04:08,940 --> 02:04:10,470
我只是想說我得找個方法
I'm just saying I got to find a way

2399
02:04:10,470 --> 02:04:11,970
去擺脫那個黑影, 媽媽
to get rid of that shadow, mama.

2400
02:04:11,970 --> 02:04:14,210
你就像他, 他早已佔據你的心了
You just like him. You got him in you good.

2401
02:04:14,210 --> 02:04:15,510
別說我是他, 媽媽
Don't tell me that, mama.

2402
02:04:15,510 --> 02:04:16,810
你簡直就是Troy Maxson
You Troy Maxson all over again.

2403
02:04:16,810 --> 02:04:19,210
我不想成為Troy Maxson!
I don't want to be Troy Maxson!

2404
02:04:20,510 --> 02:04:22,150
我只想做我自己
I just want to be me.

2405
02:04:22,150 --> 02:04:25,150
你永遠都會是你自己啊, Cory
You can't be nobody but who you are, Cory.

2406
02:04:25,150 --> 02:04:28,490
那黑影只不過是你自己製造出來的
That shadow wasn't nothing but you growing into yourself.

2407
02:04:28,490 --> 02:04:30,490
