and sometimes, when he took me in his arms, he cut.

2418
02:05:07,190 --> 02:05:09,360
我最初遇見你爸爸時
When I first met your daddy,

2419
02:05:10,260 --> 02:05:12,030
我在想
I thought,

2420
02:05:12,030 --> 02:05:15,170
那是個我可以付託終身的人
"here is a man I can lay down with and make a baby."

2421
02:05:18,840 --> 02:05:21,840
那就是我對他的第一個想法
That's the first thing I thought when I seen him.

2422
02:05:21,840 --> 02:05:24,110
我當時想: Rose Lee
I thought, "Rose Lee,

